snippet.title: DIVE: Starpath Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
DIVE: Starpath is a 3D level-based runner set in the stratosphere of massive planets. Come with elite Diver Juno as she traverses across a foreign star system in pursuit of a mysterious traveler. Dodge interstellar debris, gather data blackboxes, and fight the pull of gravity as you soar, spin, and dive through deep space.


Curious about Gravity Well Studios? Check us out here; 
http://www.gravitywellstudios.com

For updates you can check out our blog at
http://www.gravitywellstudios.com/blog

Follow us on Twitter! http://www.twitter.com/divestarpath

Like us on Facebook! http://www.facebook.com/divegame

Featuring music by https://soundcloud.com/nick-borrego 
https://www.facebook.com/Nick-Borrego...
